---
source: crates/pixi_manifest/src/toml/manifest.rs
expression: "expect_parse_failure(r#\"\n        [workspace]\n        channels = []\n        platforms = []\n\n        [constraints]\n        my-package = { path = \"../my-package\" }\n        \"#,)"
---
  × source specifications are not supported in `[constraints]`, but 'my-package' is a source specification
   ╭─[pixi.toml:7:22]
 6 │         [constraints]
 7 │         my-package = { path = "../my-package" }
   ·                      ─────────────┬────────────
   ·                                   ╰── source specification specified here
 8 │
   ╰────
  help: constraints only apply to packages resolved from channels, not source packages
